(10) An information processing method including:
obtaining first transmission control information;
obtaining second transmission control information similar to information input to another transmitter apparatus;
processing transmission target data based on a parameter contained in the first transmission control information; and
generating data including the processed transmission target data and the second transmission control information.

(11) A program causing a computer to execute a process including:
obtaining first transmission control information;
obtaining second transmission control information similar to information input to another transmitter apparatus;
processing transmission target data based on a parameter contained in the first transmission control information; and
generating data including the processed transmission target data and the second transmission control information.

